00:10:38.790 --> 00:10:42.310
Another solution is to
pretend that your

00:10:42.310 --> 00:10:43.570
differences are flukes.

00:10:43.570 --> 00:10:47.430
This is an early Superboy
cartoon when he lifts a car to

00:10:47.430 --> 00:10:48.700
save someone.

00:10:48.700 --> 00:10:50.070
And his friends see.

00:10:50.070 --> 00:10:51.400
And they're wowed.

00:10:51.400 --> 00:10:54.170
And he says, I guess something
happened just for a minute to

00:10:54.170 --> 00:10:55.910
give me super strength.

00:10:55.910 --> 00:10:56.800
Right?

