And people do actually exhibit
super strength when there are

00:10:59.670 --> 00:11:03.180
emergencies like this, so OK.

00:11:03.180 --> 00:11:06.520
Another solution, which is the
one that I advocate, is to

00:11:06.520 --> 00:11:11.040
accept and, if possible,
enjoy being different.

00:11:11.040 --> 00:11:13.750
And that when you're by
yourself, or with family and

00:11:13.750 --> 00:11:17.290
friends who are supportive,
being different can be a

00:11:17.290 --> 00:11:18.960
positive force.

00:11:18.960 --> 00:11:23.210
So this is Superboy being alone
and having fun just

00:11:23.210 --> 00:11:29.130
